[ a                      owl:Axiom ;
  rdfs:comment           "Provides Input For Rule. The relation 'ABCE1:ATP binds PELO:HBS1L-1:GTP:80S ribosome:non-stop mRNA:peptidyl-tRNA with nascent peptide and HBS1L-1:GDP is released' 'null' 'ABCE1:PELO:80S Ribosome:non-stop mRNA:peptidyl-tRNA with elongating peptide dissociates yielding ABCE1:40S ribosomal subunit, PELO, and 60S ribosomal subunit:peptidyl-tRNA with nascent peptide' was inferred because:\n reaction1 has an output that is an input of reaction 2. " , "Imported from Reactome: https://reactome.org/content/detail/R-HSA-9954714" ;
